---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout locale="en" title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="container policy-page">
    <a href="/" class="link-back" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.375rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-size:0.875rem">
      ← Back to Home
    </a>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="policy-updated">Last updated: March 2025</p>
    <div class="policy-content">
      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information you provide directly, such as name, email address, shipping address, and payment information when you make a purchase.</p>
      <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use your information to process orders, send order confirmations, provide customer support, and send promotional emails (with your consent).</p>
      <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your personal information. We share information only with service providers necessary to operate our business (payment processors, shipping carriers).</p>
      <h2>Data Security</h2>
      <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information. All payment transactions are encrypted via SSL.</p>
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>For privacy-related questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@pokestopmtl.com" style="color:var(--accent)">info@pokestopmtl.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
